data.text: @Potszicle It’s still early and fresh for them. Michael and I would do this but privately and then one day you’re over it, because you know. And they know.

@anattack001 It was thick. Like... kinda when Seal and Hiedi renewed their vows every year. When it's too much, it's almost like you're convincing yourself you love one another. I mean, thank you for loving me but let a bitch breathe. But three years together, this should come every decade 😂
